---
title: Sticky-Sweet BBQ Chicken Thighs with Sweet Potato Wedges and Ranch
description: Sweet and smoky = delicious! Our addictive BBQ seasoning and sweet chili sauce make a sticky glaze for chicken thighs. Dip the chicken and wedges in creamy, dreamy ranch!
